#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.to_numeric.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.to\\_numeric"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:1 of
msgid "Convert argument to a numeric type."
msgstr "将参数转换为数值类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:3 of
msgid ""
"The default return dtype is `float64` or `int64` depending on the data "
"supplied. Use the `downcast` parameter to obtain other dtypes."
msgstr ""
"默认返回的 dtype 是 `float64` 或 `int64`，取决于提供的数据。使用 `"
"downcast` 参数可以获得其他 dtype。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:7 of
msgid ""
"Please note that precision loss may occur if really large numbers are "
"passed in. Due to the internal limitations of `ndarray`, if numbers "
"smaller than `-9223372036854775808` (np.iinfo(np.int64).min) or larger "
"than `18446744073709551615` (np.iinfo(np.uint64).max) are passed in, it "
"is very likely they will be converted to float so that they can stored in"
" an `ndarray`. These warnings apply similarly to `Series` since it "
"internally leverages `ndarray`."
msgstr ""
"请注意，如果传入非常大的数字，可能会发生精度丢失。由于 `ndarray` 的内部"
"限制，如果传入小于 `-9223372036854775808` (np.iinfo(np.int64).min) 或大于"
" `18446744073709551615` (np.iinfo(np.uint64).max) 的数字，很可能会被转换"
"为 float 以便存储在 `ndarray` 中。这些警告同样适用于 `Series`，因为它内部"
"使用了 `ndarray`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:15 of
msgid "Argument to be converted."
msgstr "要转换的参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:17 of
msgid ""
"- If 'raise', then invalid parsing will raise an exception. - If "
"'coerce', then invalid parsing will be set as NaN. - If 'ignore', then "
"invalid parsing will return the input."
msgstr ""
"- 如果为 'raise'，则无效解析将引发异常。 - 如果为 'coerce'，则无效解析将"
"被设置为 NaN。 - 如果为 'ignore'，则无效解析将返回输入。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:18 of
msgid "If 'raise', then invalid parsing will raise an exception."
msgstr "如果为 'raise'，则无效解析将引发异常。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:19 of
msgid "If 'coerce', then invalid parsing will be set as NaN."
msgstr "如果为 'coerce'，则无效解析将被设置为 NaN。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:20 of
msgid "If 'ignore', then invalid parsing will return the input."
msgstr "如果为 'ignore'，则无效解析将返回输入。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:22 of
msgid ""
"If not None, and if the data has been successfully cast to a numerical "
"dtype (or if the data was numeric to begin with), downcast that resulting"
" data to the smallest numerical dtype possible according to the following"
" rules:  - 'integer' or 'signed': smallest signed int dtype (min.: "
"np.int8) - 'unsigned': smallest unsigned int dtype (min.: np.uint8) - "
"'float': smallest float dtype (min.: np.float32)  As this behaviour is "
"separate from the core conversion to numeric values, any errors raised "
"during the downcasting will be surfaced regardless of the value of the "
"'errors' input.  In addition, downcasting will only occur if the size of "
"the resulting data's dtype is strictly larger than the dtype it is to be "
"cast to, so if none of the dtypes checked satisfy that specification, no "
"downcasting will be performed on the data."
msgstr ""
"如果不为 None，并且数据已成功转换为数值类型（或者数据本身就是数值类型），"
"则根据以下规则将结果数据向下转换为可能的最小数值类型： - 'integer' 或 '"
"signed'：最小的有符号整数类型（最小值：np.int8） - 'unsigned'：最小的无"
"符号整数类型（最小值：np.uint8） - 'float'：最小的浮点数类型（最小值：np."
"float32） 由于此行为与核心数值转换是分开的，因此在向下转换期间引发的任何"
"错误都会被抛出，而不管 'errors' 输入的值是什么。 此外，仅当结果数据的 "
"dtype 大小严格大于要转换到的 dtype 时才会发生向下转换，因此如果没有满足该"
"规范的 dtype，则不会对数据执行向下转换。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:22 of
msgid ""
"If not None, and if the data has been successfully cast to a numerical "
"dtype (or if the data was numeric to begin with), downcast that resulting"
" data to the smallest numerical dtype possible according to the following"
" rules:"
msgstr ""
"如果不为 None，并且如果数据已成功转换为数值类型（或数据最初就是数值类型）"
"，则根据以下规则将结果数据向下转换为最小的数值类型："

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:27 of
msgid "'integer' or 'signed': smallest signed int dtype (min.: np.int8)"
msgstr "'integer' 或 'signed'：最小的有符号整数类型（最小值：np.int8）"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:28 of
msgid "'unsigned': smallest unsigned int dtype (min.: np.uint8)"
msgstr "'unsigned'：最小的无符号整数类型（最小值：np.uint8）"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:29 of
msgid "'float': smallest float dtype (min.: np.float32)"
msgstr "'float'：最小的浮点类型（最小值：np.float32）"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:31 of
msgid ""
"As this behaviour is separate from the core conversion to numeric values,"
" any errors raised during the downcasting will be surfaced regardless of "
"the value of the 'errors' input."
msgstr ""
"由于此行为与核心的数值转换是分开的，因此在向下转换期间引发的任何错误都将"
"被显示，而不管 'errors' 输入的值如何。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:35 of
msgid ""
"In addition, downcasting will only occur if the size of the resulting "
"data's dtype is strictly larger than the dtype it is to be cast to, so if"
" none of the dtypes checked satisfy that specification, no downcasting "
"will be performed on the data."
msgstr ""
"此外，只有当结果数据类型的大小严格大于要转换的数据类型时，才会进行向下"
"转换，因此如果不检查的任何数据类型满足该规范，则不会对数据执行向下转换。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.to_numeric.to_numeric:42 of
msgid ""
"Numeric if parsing succeeded. Return type depends on input.  Series if "
"Series, otherwise Tensor."
msgstr ""
"如果解析成功则返回数值。返回类型取决于输入。如果是 Series 则返回 Series，"
"否则返回 Tensor。"

